Parasite appeared!?

That's the monster that preys on
the BQ1053 small Titan Parasites.

rows.label: qst105307_msg0003

It's out of season for them
to be around here, but...

rows.label: qst105307_msg0004

small Titan Parasites must
have attracted it.

rows.label: qst105307_msg0005
rows.name:
At any rate, the abnormally
large number of monsters has
returned to normal. Thank you.

cooperation would be a great help.

accept this as our gratitude.
